      "review_summary": "The PR changes context-window resolution so status and gateway startup kick off model catalog/cache warming, delegates status summary to the shared context resolver, converts context catalog imports to static imports, and updates related tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +14, Tests +136. Total +150 across 8 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the PR defect from source inspection: the added tests themselves show the first status-style call returning 200_000 before warmup is flushed. No live cold-start command was run in this read-only review.",
